
Overview of noun confrontation

The noun confrontation has 5 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                  
1. (1) confrontation -- (a bold challenge)
2. confrontation -- (discord resulting from a clash of ideas or opinions)
3. confrontation, encounter, showdown, face-off -- (a hostile disagreement face-to-face)
4. confrontation, opposition -- (the act of hostile groups opposing each other; "the government was not ready for a confrontation with the unions"; "the invaders encountered stiff opposition")
5. confrontation -- (a focussed comparison; bringing together for a careful comparison)
